{"type": "article", "id": 16786, "title": "像这15条那样刷屏，包你没朋友丨好奇心研究所", "description": "啊哈，我不是说你，别走啊，真不是说你……", "date": "2015-10-29T15:32:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11405, "name": "好奇心研究所"}], "category": 3, "column": 33, "author": 112725, "comment_count": 24, "praise_count": 113, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021346150fJsekGWBna7l2Sj.JPG", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>好奇心研究所的微博（</span><a href=\"http://weibo.com/p/1006065587974982/home?from=page_100606&amp;mod=TAB#place\" target=\"_blank\">@好奇心研究所</a><span>）和微信公众号（ID：</span><span>QLab42</span><span>）全面上线啦，微信直接搜索「好奇心研究所」就可以订阅，关注与所长亲密接触，赶紧的。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><span></span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t1.  每天更新动态 10 条及以上\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134605UK06DfgzZ3JePXkw.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t2.  单调恒久远，百年如一日\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134606pfQgGdyHVAmqRTCJ.gif\" width=\"370\" height=\"267\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.72162162\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t3.  万物皆自拍（@果粒橙）\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134606po0YkbXRjKmPJc45.gif\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t4.  凡事都“卧槽”\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134607bNqlugjzyBawnx3A.gif\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t5.  代购\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134607AGwRBx5pqQ8fPjLM.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"248\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.496\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t6.  文艺腔\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134608kb23G5JX4dtcBpjQ.gif\" width=\"250\" height=\"192\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.768\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t7.  习大大，彭麻麻\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134608mDya9u54zNFWhClv.gif\" width=\"400\" height=\"225\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t8.  救救孩子\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021346093uHlIPpUzVDL07BQ.gif\" width=\"400\" height=\"223\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.5575\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t9.  为父母/好运/抽奖一定要转\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021346106j1zsSkfDBwq0ZIy.gif\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.56333333\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t10.  只要偶像发声，无脑狂转 N 条\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134610qhdcY3i89uQWgD1O.gif\" width=\"480\" height=\"292\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.60833333\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t11.  XX 岁一定要知道的 X 件事\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134611nCp5zA4fvQsc6ay2.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t12.  不转不是中国人（@姆明谷黑魔导士）\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134612XilKT0GgQUFj7zSY.gif\" width=\"320\" height=\"180\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t13.  请投我邻居家的二狗的外甥的弟弟 7 号一票哦耶\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134613ItmeCHQ6uvrw9GLO.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"350\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t14.  晒娃，还是小视频，还接连发五六七八九个……（@蕙竹）\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021346132JSLvQpAU0KIPMl9.gif\" width=\"356\" height=\"200\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.56179775\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t15.  晒你那送谁谁都不要的对象。在所有能刷屏的日子。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134614EyGqIKQaM7sf5Vk9.gif\" width=\"506\" height=\"253\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span><strong>以上条目均来自「好奇心研究所」我说栏目与微信公众号征集，你可以</strong></span><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/mobs/594.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>在这里继续参与讨论</strong></a><span><strong>。</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}